      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Six runners, six chances. KNIGHTS ARMOUR (3) started his run a long way out and kept finding to get up for fourth last start over 2200m at this track. Is a winner at the mile-and-a-half and showed last time that he is ready to find peak form after four runs back from a spell. MAJORIAN (4) has been safely held in his two runs this prep, both over much shorter journeys. Scored twice over 2200m at this track last prep, the latest win under a 60kg steadier. Should be about to hit his straps. DE LOUVIERE (6) is a genuine stayer who gave away a huge start before closing the gap to 1.3 lengths behind STYLEBENDER over 2200m here recently. Scored here at this distance the run before and with the light weight makes plenty of appeal. CASUAL CONNECTION (1) has four 2400m wins to his name, including two from two attempts at Warwick Farm. Excellent effort to finish second last time over 1800m. Key contender. Last start Wyong winner AUTUMN WINTER (5) is lightly raced and progressing in good style.",
